  <packageId>Rockets.Airstrike</packageId>
  <description>Adds an airstrike gizmo to aerial vehicles. The vehicle takes off, makes a bombing pass over a chosen cell on the same map, then returns to its origin. Built on Vehicle Framework.</description>
